			  	PP income assigned to build ships(per turn)= how much of the money you invest goes into making a ship, and if you aint got any ships being made it goes into Invested PP Left part<br />
<br />
PP in Ship Production Pool=how much a ship has been build, if you got 21,045,307 in it and 10million goes into ship pool a turn a doom would take 1 more turn to build<br />
<br />
Invested PP Left=how much of the money you invest from your bank and any left over cash from your domestic-page/ship-pool thing goes into this<br />
<br />
Maximum PP Usage per Turn=same as your ship-pool/domestic thing,its how much money from your overall production goes into making ships<br />
<br />
holy crap nothing could be wrong with this hurray			   <P align=right></P>
